\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

Standalone-Muon track only
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 is claimed, if both previous described methods fail.
 This is the case if the muon is observed only in the muon system.
 Due to the high tracker efficiency, those muons are often originating from
 cosmic-rays and not from an interaction at the IP 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "muonID"

\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The particle-flow algorithm categorizes the muons further.
 A muon is 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

isolated
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

